abstract: The computer networking giant supplied more evidence that tech sales are picking up as the global economy begins to recover.
snippet: The computer networking giant supplied more evidence that tech sales are picking up as the global economy begins to recover.
lead_paragraph: Cisco Systems, the computer networking giant, supplied more evidence on Wednesday that technology sales were recovering along with the global economy.

headline.main: Cisco’s Results Offer More Hope to Tech Industry
headline.print_headline: Cisco’s Results Offer More Hope to Tech Industry
